data.description: Located in the gated community of Coco Palm Estates in Homestead, this corner unit townhome offers a beautiful lakefront view and comprises of 3 bedrooms and 3 full bathrooms. There is also plenty of room to enjoy, with over 1800 square feet of living space, tile flooring on the first floor, and wood-like flooring on the second floor. The kitchen and bathrooms have been recently renovated, providing a fresh and modern look. The kitchen has new appliances, countertops, and cabinets. The bathrooms are equipped with new fixtures, vanities, and tiling, offering a contemporary and spa-like feel. The one-car garage is designed with a floor coating that provides a clean and polished appearance. For added convenience and protection, accordion shutters are installed throughout the home.
